府近期有在內地推廣香港，但佢保證唔到內地人來港不受恐嚇。」香港是法治的地方，要照法律去做，若然不跟隨就只會繼續縱容暴徒行為，客人不來港的責任又誰來負責，所以「唔好將嗰責任推俾政府，政府唔係萬能，只要唔嚇人、唔打人，大家咪無事囉。」<br />\n<br />\n不過他重申，目前的零售情況對公司業務影響不大，皆因旗下在港商場商戶主要以民生為主，內地商場則主打奢侈品，並看好上海以外地區未來的增長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/財經/陳啟宗：黑衣人恐嚇內地客-零售難復高增長-204598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%2F%E9%99%B3%E5%95%9F%E5%AE%97%EF%BC%9A%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2-%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E9%9B%A3%E5%BE%A9%E9%AB%98%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7-204598&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6gVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=2e237d00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/財經/陳啟宗：黑衣人恐嚇內地客-零售難復高增長-204598</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"而家個蛋糕係我地整，只係唔比你食"},{"pid":"3de645e039c733ff40cfd06098f5b117943783ed","tid":1832576,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb5d34448e8a10b65f1843b97b47eb0f70279546","tid":1832576,"uid":998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問題核心 點解要谷高香港零售？<br />\n得果1% GDP 擾民到仆街</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AJU5BH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AJU5BH.png&h=d1588fce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff6f1f05e0727328f2b2f9eb5d3df9a76592292b","tid":1832576,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:02:43.000Z","msg":"萬一商場有病毒，就冇人會去。"},{"pid":"a37639c30c97170dc09bc300a74f4abd798d7d58","tid":1832576,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"玩地產咁多年仲未入四大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d8088d035b983cbc11194b7998ab47f9ecd82c","tid":1832576,"uid":292710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb5d34448e8a10